208
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,880
You're right.

209
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,720
Now that I'm about to be
the Prince Consort,

210
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,520
I'll take Her Highness's side.

211
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,120
Her Highness won't go easy

212
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:33,440
on the criminals
of the embezzlement case.

213
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:35,360
If you don't turn back,

214
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:38,000
